  "boundaryRules": [
    "Console calls only Control Plane product APIs.",
    "Control Plane orchestrates typed Fabric, Ledger, and Sub2API clients without exposing generic proxy routes.",
    "Implemented route means the current commercial route contract names page, API client, server API intent, service boundary, object kind, and permissions; runtime migration must remove retired compatibility routes before merge.",
