    "External routes are current integration entry points and must name the external URL or integration boundary.",
    "Active route contract contains only current commercial truth; future, reserved, and prune candidates live in route backlog.",
    "Every enabled route has a stable route id used by menus, actions, and routeTo().",
    "Lab Owner routes expose business outcomes; Admin routes expose operator evidence and operations.",
    "Operator summary machine token is accepted only through x-opl-operator-token; query-string operatorToken is forbidden.",
